name: Bron Tapes BT-279S AV Cord Tape
description: Bron Tapes BT-279S AV Cord Tape is clean removal, conformable, hand-tearable, low tack for more delicate surfaces, and high quality. Ideal for temporary fixing and holding of wires and cables, masking and marking of stage equipment, floor marking stages and film sets, color coding and identification, and spine binding. BT-279S features a quality matte finish, with low/no light reflection.
